  https://github.com/hellofresh/health-go

The original work has been substantially modified with the following additions:
- Background health check execution (prevents DoS to backend services)
- Notification system with configurable notifiers
- Action runners for automated responses to health state changes
- Event tracking for incident correlation
- Maintenance mode support
- Status thresholds (SuccessesBeforePassing, FailuresBeforeWarning, FailuresBeforeCritical)
- Check pause/resume functionality

